docs {
  ### Create Credit Limit Transaction
  Creates a new credit limit transaction. Transactions are immutable — no update allowed.
  Restricted to Admin / Super Admin.

  **transactionType:** DEBIT | CREDIT | TEMP_LIMIT | ADJUSTMENT
  **userType:** client | vendor
  **referenceType:** Booking | Payment | Limit Allotment
}
